Enrollment Requirements: REASON: Pre-registration is not allowed for this class. Please try again during regular registration.

Students must have completed EECS 214, and either EECS 213 or EECS 205, or have PhD standing in CS to register for this course. Students must also be willing to learn the Java programming language and be comfortable working in a command line interface.
